caption:
Breaking up is hard, but teaming up with your ex? That’s a whole new recipe for chaos 😬 Four ex-couples reunite (and rehash old drama) in the #Chopped Hungry for Love tournament! Can old flames handle the heat — or will someone get burned? 🔥💔

Tune in TONIGHT @ 8|7c to see which team moves on for a shot at $50K!
